  </div>
</button>
<div class="panel yellow">
  <div class="text-details">
    <h3>Details & care</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><b>Features:</b> 340 pages, linen hard cover</li>
      <li><b>Published by:</b> Gestalten</li>
      <li><b>Printed in:</b> Germany</li>
      <li><b>Dimensions:</b> 20cm x 26.5cm x 3cm
